\begin{center}
    \textbf{INTRODUCTION}
\end{center}

\vspace{0.8cm}

\noindent
I am Mahabub Alam Tamim, and I am currently pursuing my Bachelor of Science in Computer Science and Engineering at Green University of Bangladesh (GUB). I have completed most of my academic coursework with satisfactory results and have gained practical knowledge through both academic projects and professional experience. My time at this university has played a significant role in shaping my technical skills, discipline, and professional mindset.

\vspace{0.4cm}

\noindent
I live in Dhaka, and my academic journey has been strongly influenced by my interest in technology and problem-solving. From an early stage of my education, I have been inclined toward computing and software development. Over the years, I have developed a strong passion for application development, system design, and learning modern technologies related to software engineering.

\vspace{0.4cm}

\noindent
After completing my undergraduate degree, I plan to pursue higher studies in Computer Science and Engineering. I am particularly interested in advanced topics related to software engineering, system architecture, and emerging technologies. Studying at an international institution will allow me to gain exposure to a multicultural academic environment, collaborate with diverse individuals, and access advanced research facilities, which will enhance the quality of my education.

\vspace{0.4cm}

\noindent
My long-term career goal is to build a strong professional profile as a skilled software engineer and contribute meaningfully to the technology sector. I am committed to continuous learning and professional growth, and I aspire to work in challenging environments where innovation, creativity, and technical excellence are encouraged. I believe that dedication, ethical practice, and lifelong learning are essential for success in the field of computer science.



